features: 【Modern Simple Style】The office desk comes in a variety of colors and sizes to suit different styles. It is minimalistic and can be matched with various settings. This home office desk is suitable for various users, including kids, teens, students as a home study table, as well as teachers as a home office desk.

【Multi-functional Storage】The small computer desk is equipped with side storage bag and hooks. The storage pockets can be used to store miscellaneous items, books, files, and more. The hooks are perfect for hanging headphones, umbrellas, and other items, ensuring a tidy desktop.
【Premium Materials】The desktop of the writing desk is made of thick particle board, providing effective scratch and water resistance to protect it from daily damage.

【Sturdy Structure】The black gaming desk is made of steel frame and reinforced with a triangular connection design, increasing stability. Rubber foot pads are included to prevent the desk from moving on different surfaces.Note: No language errors were detected in the provided translation.
【Convenient Assembly】 We provide detailed instructions and installation tools to help you assemble quickly. If you have any questions, you can contact us and we will reply within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this table! Very Sturdy and Easy to put together and looks great!
reviews.reviewText: This table is extremely sturdy. You can use it for computers, writing, art, gaming systems, etc. It was very easy to put together. It looks really nice. One side has a soft sided holder for files, paperwork or whatever you need. Nice side too. Most tables are just too big and this one is just perfect for smaller spaces. You still have a nice size work area - almost 32" x almost 20. Great price too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Excellent small space desk
reviews.reviewText: We had a pretty small space that we could fit a desk and didn’t have many options. After weeks of measuring and looking at different options we settled on this one. We liked it came in different finished to fit best with many difference styles.It was on sale and for the price we could beat it, even if we didn’t like it we could use for other things. Putting together was super easy about 30 minutes with one person. All hardware was accounted for which is always a plus.We got into the space and it was perfect size!We only got it for occasional working from home for small increments. I defiantly wouldn’t say this is for someone that needs multiple monitors and works from home everyday. We just have a small laptop and keyboard and it fits great with enough space for a small pad to take notes.We are pretty happy with the purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good table. good price.
reviews.reviewText: I got mine for about $60, which was a steal. shipping said it would come next week, about 5 days, but I got mine in 3 days. nice. no scratches or damage, and everything was there.setup could have been made a little easier by them just circling that the holes for the corner bracket on the leg and horizontal support must line up, they just give you a picture and say this one on this side and this one on the other side, but that doesn't help dyslexic people like me. just circle the holes and say they gotta line up for the corner bracket.really sturdy table, does not move much when I try to shake it. the corners and edges are a little more sharp than other tables I've used but for $60, you cant complain at all. usually a table this size and weight capacity would easily cost $90+

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My 40 inch desk arrived today. I put it together in about 45 mins. Very easy, sturdy and fits perfectly in the space I measured it for. All I do is pay bills and plan vacations on my lap top computer so I didn't need a lot of space. I love it. Great find and it's doesn't look cheap. Love the color as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Is it my value for the money? Sorta, hard to tell.Im using it for what I intended to and its too just hold my moderately sized computer off the ground. Its not that stable, you can move it move a little when the cats climb on it, became even less stable when I put furniture sliders under it. That cloth pouch thing was impossible to put on. I would have to unsewn it to cut the cardbord inside and then sew it back up cause its so long it pushes the screw holes too low. All in all, it does what I need which is thankfully a very simple request. But for how much it cost? Not really worth it, I should of looked around more.
